<search>
  <entry>
    <title>Matplotlib</title>
    <url>/2022/09/05/Matplotlib/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="导入模块"><a href="#导入模块" class="headerlink" title="导入模块"></a>导入模块</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%matplotlib inline</span><br><span class="line">%config InlineBackend.figure_format = <span class="string">&#x27;svg&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="自定义配置文件"><a href="#自定义配置文件" class="headerlink" title="自定义配置文件"></a>自定义配置文件</h2><p>rcParams 中存储了 Matplotlib 绘图时所有参数的默认值，在 matplotlibrc 文件中。</p>
<p>可通过字典的形式来修改 rcParams:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">config = &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;font.family&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;Times New Roman&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">&#x27;font.size&#x27;</span>: <span class="number">15</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">&#x27;xtick.direction&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;in&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">&#x27;ytick.direction&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;in&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">&#x27;mathtext.fontset&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;stix&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="string">&#x27;savefig.dpi&#x27;</span>: <span class="number">300</span></span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">plt.rcParams.update(config)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>也可以修改单个参数:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.rcParams[<span class="string">&#x27;lines.marker&#x27;</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;^&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.rcParams[<span class="string">&#x27;lines.linestyle&#x27;</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.rcParams[<span class="string">&#x27;axes.grid&#x27;</span>] = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.rcParams[<span class="string">&#x27;font.family&#x27;</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;Kaiti&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="绘图风格"><a href="#绘图风格" class="headerlink" title="绘图风格"></a>绘图风格</h2><p>绘图风格 (style) 即上述参数已经组装好的预设方案，从而可快速配置。</p>
<p>matplotlib.pyplot 中有多个已经配置好的 style，在 stylelib 文件夹中。</p>
<p>可以打印出可用的预设方案以供选择:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(plt.style.available)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>可以采用全局或局部两种方式调用绘图风格。对于全局配置，只需申明:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.style.use(<span class="string">&#x27;ggplot&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment"># 使用 ggplot 风格</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>每次全局调用，都会覆盖上一次的 style。</p>
<p>对于局部配置，可使用 with 代码块:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> plt.style.context(<span class="string">&#x27;ggplot&#x27;</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    plt.subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.plot([-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样即能保证其 style 只在 with 代码块内被调用。</p>
<p>此外，也可以清除所有调用的 style。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">matplotlib.rc_file_defaults()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>除了默认的预设方案，也可以自定义 style。</p>
<p>如，首先在 stylelib 文件夹中创建 wangstyle.mplstyle 文件。然后写入:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Matplotlib style for my plotting</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">xtick.direction: <span class="keyword">in</span></span><br><span class="line">ytick.direction: <span class="keyword">in</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">font.family: Times New Roman</span><br><span class="line">font.size: 15</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>有一个科学绘图的风格可用于借鉴:  <a href="https://github.com/garrettj403/SciencePlots">SciencePlots</a>。</p>
<h2 id="Anatomy-of-a-figure"><a href="#Anatomy-of-a-figure" class="headerlink" title="Anatomy of a figure"></a>Anatomy of a figure</h2><p>Matplotlib 各成分之间的关系:</p>
<p><img src="https://matplotlib.org/stable/_images/sphx_glr_anatomy_001_2_0x.png" alt="Anatomy of a figure"></p>
<h2 id="API"><a href="#API" class="headerlink" title="API"></a>API</h2><p>在 Matplotlib 中，有三种画图方式:  </p>
<ul>
<li>The Pyplot API，通过 plt.xx 来画图。本质上是利用 matplotlib 提供的一个 api。好处在于简单，画图方式接近于 Matlab，坏处在于自定义程度不够。</li>
<li>The Object-Oriented API，即面向对象绘图。</li>
<li>The pylab API，不过这种官方不推荐。</li>
</ul>
<p>以下是一个完全由 Pyplot API 组成的案例。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">m = np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">50</span>)</span><br><span class="line">n1 = np.random.rand(<span class="number">50</span>)</span><br><span class="line">n2 = np.random.rand(<span class="number">50</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">4</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(m, n1)</span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(m, n2, color=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, linewidth=<span class="number">1.0</span>, linestyle=<span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.grid()</span><br><span class="line">plt.xlim((<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.ylim((<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.xticks(np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.xlabel(<span class="string">&#x27;I am x&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.ylabel(<span class="string">&#x27;I am y&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;Times New Roman&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.tick_params(direction=<span class="string">&#x27;in&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># plt.savefig(&#x27;pltchuangtong.svg&#x27;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Object-Oriented API 有三种画法（大同小异），主要体现在画布和子图的创建上。分别为:  </p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第一种</span></span><br><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">3</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax1 = fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax2 = fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第二种</span></span><br><span class="line">fig, ax = plt.subplots(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, figsize=(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax1 = ax[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">ax1 = ax[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第三种（第三种子图其实是调用了 Pyplot API）</span></span><br><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize = (<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">3</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax = plt.subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这三种画法中: 第三种属于 Pyplot API 与面向对象画法混用。第二种是第一种的简略画法，但在绘制极坐标图和三维图等特殊类型时并不好用。一般推荐前两种绘图方式。</p>
<h2 id="子图布局"><a href="#子图布局" class="headerlink" title="子图布局"></a>子图布局</h2><p>可以使用 subplots_adjust 来调整子图布局。其六个参数范围均在 [0, 1] 之间。</p>
<p>其中，top, bottom, left, right 围住的区域即每个子图的区域。hspace 和 wspace 代表子图间的间距。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.subplots_adjust(top    = <span class="literal">None</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    bottom = <span class="literal">None</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    left   = <span class="literal">None</span>, </span><br><span class="line">                    right  = <span class="literal">None</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    hspace = <span class="literal">None</span>, <span class="comment"># 上下间距</span></span><br><span class="line">                    wspace = <span class="literal">None</span>) <span class="comment"># 左右间距</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>对于特殊的不规则布局，可以借用 gridspec 来配置，如:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.gridspec <span class="keyword">as</span> gridspec</span><br><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">10</span>))</span><br><span class="line">gs = gridspec.GridSpec(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)      <span class="comment"># 设 3 行 3 列</span></span><br><span class="line">ax1 = fig.add_subplot(gs[<span class="number">0</span>, :])   <span class="comment"># 第 1 行，所有列</span></span><br><span class="line">ax2 = fig.add_subplot(gs[<span class="number">1</span>, :-<span class="number">1</span>]) <span class="comment"># 第 2 行，前 2 列</span></span><br><span class="line">ax3 = fig.add_subplot(gs[<span class="number">1</span>:, -<span class="number">1</span>]) <span class="comment"># 后 2 行，第 3 列</span></span><br><span class="line">ax4 = fig.add_subplot(gs[<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>])   <span class="comment"># 第 3 行，第 1 列</span></span><br><span class="line">ax5 = fig.add_subplot(gs[<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>])   <span class="comment"># 第 3 行，第 2 列</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="坐标轴-Axis-Spine"><a href="#坐标轴-Axis-Spine" class="headerlink" title="坐标轴 Axis / Spine"></a>坐标轴 Axis / Spine</h2><p>坐标轴颜色与隐藏</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># top, bottom, left, right</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;top&#x27;</span>].set_color(<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>].set_color(<span class="string">&#x27;none&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>移动坐标轴</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;bottom&#x27;</span>].set_position((<span class="string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>].set_position((<span class="string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">0.2</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>轴标签名</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.xlabel(<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.ylabel(<span class="string">&#x27;y&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xlabel(<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.set_ylabel(<span class="string">&#x27;y&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>坐标轴科学计数法</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.ticklabel_format(axis=<span class="string">&quot;y&quot;</span>, style=<span class="string">&quot;sci&quot;</span>, scilimits=(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="刻度-Tick"><a href="#刻度-Tick" class="headerlink" title="刻度 Tick"></a>刻度 Tick</h2><p>刻度范围</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.axis([-<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, -<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>])  </span><br><span class="line">plt.xlim(-<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">6</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.ylim(-<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xlim(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">8</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.set_ylim(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">26</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>刻度间隔</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.xticks([<span class="number">22282</span>, <span class="number">26665</span>, <span class="number">31048</span>], labels = [<span class="string">&#x27;1961&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;1973&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;1985&#x27;</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xticks(np.linspace(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">4</span>)) <span class="comment"># 空为无刻度</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_yticks(np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">25</span>,<span class="number">5</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.ticker <span class="keyword">import</span> MultipleLocator</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义 x 刻度差为 2 的倍数</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(MultipleLocator(<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义 y 刻度差为 3 的倍数</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.yaxis.set_major_locator(MultipleLocator(<span class="number">3</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>刻度标签</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.set_xticklabels([<span class="string">&#x27;子&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;丑&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;寅&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;卯&#x27;</span>]) <span class="comment"># 设置刻度标签</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_yticklabels([<span class="string">&#x27;甲&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;乙&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;丙&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;丁&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;戊&#x27;</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>参数刻度线样式</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.tick_params(axis=<span class="string">&#x27;both&#x27;</span>,      <span class="comment"># &#x27;x&#x27;, &#x27;y&#x27;, &#x27;both&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">               which=<span class="string">&#x27;major&#x27;</span>,    <span class="comment"># 主副刻度 &#x27;major&#x27;, &#x27;minor&#x27;, &#x27;both&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">               reset=<span class="literal">False</span>,      <span class="comment"># 是否重置之前的所有刻度设置</span></span><br><span class="line">               direction=<span class="string">&#x27;in&#x27;</span>,   <span class="comment"># 刻度方向 &#x27;in&#x27;, &#x27;out&#x27;, &#x27;inout&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">               length=<span class="number">1.0</span>,       <span class="comment"># 刻度长度</span></span><br><span class="line">               width=<span class="number">1.0</span>,        <span class="comment"># 刻度宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">               color=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>,      <span class="comment"># 刻度颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">               pad=<span class="number">1.0</span>,          <span class="comment"># 刻度线和标签的距离</span></span><br><span class="line">               labelsize=<span class="number">1.0</span>,    <span class="comment"># 刻度标签大小</span></span><br><span class="line">               labelcolor=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, <span class="comment"># 刻度标签颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">               colors=<span class="literal">None</span>,      <span class="comment"># 刻度和标签的颜色，一起设置</span></span><br><span class="line">               zorder=<span class="number">1.0</span>,       <span class="comment"># 未理解</span></span><br><span class="line">               bottom=<span class="literal">True</span>,      <span class="comment"># 是否绘制相应位置刻度</span></span><br><span class="line">               top=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               left=<span class="literal">True</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               right=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               labelbottom=<span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="comment"># 是否显示相应位置标签</span></span><br><span class="line">               labeltop=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               labelleft=<span class="literal">True</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               labelright=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">               labelrotation=<span class="number">0.0</span>,<span class="comment"># 标签旋转角度</span></span><br><span class="line">              )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;Title&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_title(label=<span class="string">&#x27;Title&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">             y=-<span class="number">0.3</span>,        <span class="comment"># 标题纵向位置，top 轴为 1.0，y 为负将标题置于下方</span></span><br><span class="line">             loc=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>,  <span class="comment"># 标题横向位置 &#x27;center&#x27;, &#x27;left&#x27;, &#x27;right&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">             pad=<span class="number">6.0</span>,       <span class="comment"># 距离 top 轴的偏移量</span></span><br><span class="line">             fontdict       <span class="comment"># 使用字典来设置标题的文本样式</span></span><br><span class="line">            )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="网格"><a href="#网格" class="headerlink" title="网格"></a>网格</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.grid()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.grid(visible=<span class="literal">True</span>,    <span class="comment"># 从 Matplotlib 3.5 版本始，b 参数改成 visible</span></span><br><span class="line">        which=<span class="string">&#x27;major&#x27;</span>,   <span class="comment"># major (只绘制大刻度), minor (只绘制小刻度), both</span></span><br><span class="line">        axis=<span class="string">&#x27;both&#x27;</span>,     <span class="comment"># 网格轴 &#x27;x&#x27;, &#x27;y&#x27;, &#x27;both&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        alpha=<span class="number">0.5</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        color=<span class="string">&#x27;skyblue&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        linestyle=<span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        linewidth=<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">       )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="图例"><a href="#图例" class="headerlink" title="图例"></a>图例</h2><p>图例设置前，需要指定 label 参数，有两种方法:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第一种是直接在绘图函数中设置 label 值，如:</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.plot([<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>], label=<span class="string">&#x27;Inline label&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第二种方法是使用 set_label() 方法:</span></span><br><span class="line">line = ax.plot([<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>])</span><br><span class="line">line.set_label(<span class="string">&#x27;Label via method&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后即可指定图例:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.legend()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.legend(loc=<span class="string">&#x27;upper left&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &#x27;upper left&#x27;, &#x27;upper right&#x27;, &#x27;lower left&#x27;, &#x27;lower right&#x27;, &#x27;best&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="文本"><a href="#文本" class="headerlink" title="文本"></a>文本</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.text()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.text(x=<span class="number">2.8</span>,              <span class="comment"># x 轴位置</span></span><br><span class="line">        y=<span class="number">7</span>,                <span class="comment"># y 轴位置</span></span><br><span class="line">        s=<span class="string">r&#x27;$y=3\times x$&#x27;</span>, <span class="comment"># 文内容</span></span><br><span class="line">        fontdict            <span class="comment"># 文本样式字典</span></span><br><span class="line">       )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="箭头标注"><a href="#箭头标注" class="headerlink" title="箭头标注"></a>箭头标注</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.annotate(text=<span class="string">&#x27;content&#x27;</span>,  <span class="comment"># 文本标注内容</span></span><br><span class="line">            xy=(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">6</span>),       <span class="comment"># 箭头位置</span></span><br><span class="line">            xytext=(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">1.5</span>), <span class="comment"># 文本标注位置</span></span><br><span class="line">            arrowprops=<span class="built_in">dict</span>(facecolor = <span class="string">&#x27;black&#x27;</span>, shrink = <span class="number">0.05</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="保存"><a href="#保存" class="headerlink" title="保存"></a>保存</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plt.savefig(<span class="string">&#x27;save.jpg&#x27;</span>, dpi = <span class="number">300</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Bar-amp-Barh"><a href="#Bar-amp-Barh" class="headerlink" title="Bar &amp; Barh"></a>Bar &amp; Barh</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ax.bar(x,               <span class="comment"># x 轴</span></span><br><span class="line">       height,          <span class="comment"># 值</span></span><br><span class="line">       width=<span class="number">0.8</span>,       <span class="comment"># 柱状的宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">       bottom=<span class="literal">None</span>,     <span class="comment"># height 的起始值，以避免下方太长</span></span><br><span class="line">       align=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>   <span class="comment"># 轴刻度对准位置，center 为正中心，edge 为左边缘</span></span><br><span class="line">       color=<span class="string">&#x27;blue&#x27;</span>,    <span class="comment"># 颜色，可以是列表形式</span></span><br><span class="line">       edgecolor=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, <span class="comment"># bar edge 的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">       linewidth=<span class="number">0</span>,     <span class="comment"># bar edge 的宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">       tick_label,      <span class="comment"># 刻度标签，用列表表示</span></span><br><span class="line">       xerr, yerr,      <span class="comment"># 每根 bar 顶部误差条，x 为横线，y 为纵线，列表表示</span></span><br><span class="line">       ecolor=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>,    <span class="comment"># 误差条的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">       capsize=<span class="number">0</span>,       <span class="comment"># 误差栏首尾的线段长度</span></span><br><span class="line">       error_kw,        <span class="comment"># 字典表示的误差栏参数</span></span><br><span class="line">       log=<span class="literal">False</span>,       <span class="comment"># 是否用对数表示</span></span><br><span class="line">      )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.barh(y,               <span class="comment"># y 轴</span></span><br><span class="line">        width,           <span class="comment"># 值</span></span><br><span class="line">        height=<span class="number">0.8</span>,      <span class="comment"># 柱状的宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">        left=<span class="literal">None</span>        <span class="comment"># 起始值，相当于 bottom</span></span><br><span class="line">        align=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>   <span class="comment"># 轴刻度对准位置，center 为正中心，edge 为左边缘</span></span><br><span class="line">        color=<span class="string">&#x27;blue&#x27;</span>,    <span class="comment"># 颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">        edgecolor=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>, <span class="comment"># bar edge 的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">        linewidth=<span class="number">0</span>,     <span class="comment"># bar edge 的宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">        tick_label       <span class="comment"># 刻度标签，用列表表示</span></span><br><span class="line">        xerr, yerr,      <span class="comment"># 每根 bar 顶部误差条，x 为横线，y 为纵线，列表表示</span></span><br><span class="line">        ecolor=<span class="string">&#x27;red&#x27;</span>,    <span class="comment"># 误差条的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">        capsize=<span class="number">0</span>,       <span class="comment"># 误差栏首尾的线段长度</span></span><br><span class="line">        error_kw,        <span class="comment"># 字典表示的误差栏参数</span></span><br><span class="line">        log=<span class="literal">False</span>        <span class="comment"># 是否用对数表示</span></span><br><span class="line">       )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如果需要在柱状图上标注文本，则需使用 bar_label()，例如:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fig, ax = plt.subplots()</span><br><span class="line">rects = ax.bar([<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>], [<span class="number">20</span>, <span class="number">34</span>, <span class="number">30</span>])</span><br><span class="line">ax.bar_label(rects, padding=<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="Pie"><a href="#Pie" class="headerlink" title="Pie"></a>Pie</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Axes.pie(x,                  <span class="comment"># The wedge sizes</span></span><br><span class="line">         explode=<span class="literal">None</span>,       <span class="comment"># 每一块分离圆心的距离，和 x 长度一致</span></span><br><span class="line">         labels=<span class="literal">None</span>,        <span class="comment"># 数据对应标签</span></span><br><span class="line">         colors=<span class="literal">None</span>,        <span class="comment"># 颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">         autopct=<span class="literal">None</span>,       <span class="comment"># 标注值的格式，如 &#x27;%1.2f%%&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">         pctdistance=<span class="number">0.6</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         shadow=<span class="literal">False</span>,       <span class="comment"># 阴影</span></span><br><span class="line">         labeldistance=<span class="number">1.1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         startangle=<span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         radius=<span class="number">1</span>,           <span class="comment"># 半径</span></span><br><span class="line">         counterclock=<span class="literal">True</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         wedgeprops=<span class="literal">None</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         textprops=<span class="literal">None</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         center=(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>),      <span class="comment"># 中心点坐标</span></span><br><span class="line">         frame=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         rotatelabels=<span class="literal">False</span>,</span><br><span class="line">         *,</span><br><span class="line">         normalize=<span class="literal">True</span>,     <span class="comment"># 归一化与否</span></span><br><span class="line">         data=<span class="literal">None</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="极坐标"><a href="#极坐标" class="headerlink" title="极坐标"></a>极坐标</h2><p>玫瑰花图</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax = fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>, projection=<span class="string">&#x27;polar&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment"># 极坐标系</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">N = <span class="number">20</span>                                          <span class="comment"># 花瓣数量</span></span><br><span class="line">theta = np.random.normal(<span class="number">0.0</span>, <span class="number">4</span> * np.pi, N)     <span class="comment"># 相当于 x 轴</span></span><br><span class="line">radii = <span class="number">10</span> * np.random.rand(N)                  <span class="comment"># 值</span></span><br><span class="line">width = np.pi / <span class="number">4</span> * np.random.rand(N)           <span class="comment"># 花瓣宽度</span></span><br><span class="line">colors = plt.cm.viridis(radii / <span class="number">10.</span>)            <span class="comment"># 颜色</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.bar(theta, radii, width=width, bottom=<span class="number">0.0</span>, color=colors, alpha=<span class="number">0.5</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="三维图"><a href="#三维图" class="headerlink" title="三维图"></a>三维图</h2><p>三维图和极坐标一样,需要事先指定坐标系:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">8</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax = fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, projection=<span class="string">&#x27;3d&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 假设生成一组数据</span></span><br><span class="line">zdata = <span class="number">15</span> * np.random.random(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line">xdata = np.sin(zdata) + <span class="number">0.1</span> * np.random.randn(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ydata = np.cos(zdata) + <span class="number">0.1</span> * np.random.randn(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 绘制三维图</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.scatter3D(xdata, ydata, zdata, c=zdata, cmap=<span class="string">&#x27;Greens&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>还可以和平面图互动:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">X, Y = np.meshgrid(np.arange(-<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">0.25</span>), np.arange(-<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">0.25</span>)) </span><br><span class="line">Z = <span class="number">3</span> * (<span class="number">1</span>-X)**<span class="number">2</span> * np.e**(-(X**<span class="number">2</span>) - (Y+<span class="number">1</span>)**<span class="number">2</span>)- <span class="number">10</span>*(X/<span class="number">5</span> - X**<span class="number">3</span> - Y**<span class="number">5</span>)*np.e**(-X**<span class="number">2</span>-Y**<span class="number">2</span>)- <span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">3</span>*np.e**(-(X+<span class="number">1</span>)**<span class="number">2</span> - Y**<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="number">10</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax = fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1</span>, projection=<span class="string">&#x27;3d&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">m = ax.plot_surface(X, Y, Z, rstride=<span class="number">1</span>, cstride=<span class="number">1</span>, cmap=plt.get_cmap(<span class="string">&#x27;Spectral&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax.contourf(X, Y, Z, zdir=<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>, offset=-<span class="number">4</span>) <span class="comment"># offset 用来挪位置</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.contourf(X, Y, Z, zdir=<span class="string">&#x27;z&#x27;</span>, offset=-<span class="number">7</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.colorbar(m, shrink=<span class="number">0.6</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
